  "body": "### User Story\n\nAs a user, I want to mention someone I want to talk to with `@` (same as in Slack) because it is a common pattern in popular messages\n\n### Description\n\n*Type*: Feature\n\n\n*Summary*: when chatting with someone i want to highlight the person with `@` sign so the person is highlighted in the chat window and gets the notification (pinged)\n\n#### Expected behavior\n\n1. `@` mentions are implemented in a group and public chats\n2. once pinged in a group or public chat the person is highlighted visually (bold with yellow for example)\n3. once pinged in a group or public chat the person gets push notification to his mobile device\n\n#### Actual behavior\nMentions are not implemented",
